movie.title: Old Dracula
movie.description_intro: In order to revive his long hibernating bride, Vampira, Count Dracula takes blood samples from several beautiful models, but during the transfusion, Vampira's race turns from white to black.

movies.title: Killing Gunther
movies.summary: A group of eccentric assassins are fed up with Gunther, the world's greatest hitman, and decide to kill him, but their plan turns into a series of bungled encounters as Gunther seems to always be one step ahead.

movies.title: Davy Crockett and the River Pirates
movies.title_english: Davy Crockett and the River Pirates
movies.title_long: Davy Crockett and the River Pirates (1956)
movies.summary: Davy Crockett and his sidekick Georgie compete against boastful Mike Fink ("King of the River") in a boat race to New Orleans. Later, Davy and Georgie, allied with Fink, battle a group of river pirates trying to pass themselves off as Native Americans.

movies.title: The Professor
movies.summary: After learning about his terminal diagnosis, a college professor decides to live his life to the fullest by drinking, smoking and expressing real thoughts for the people around him. While going through the stages, he come to terms with the great truth of his life as he mends broken relationships, embraces the people in his life and learns to ignite his inner good spirit.

movies.title: Teen Titans Go! Vs. Teen Titans
movies.title_english: Teen Titans Go! Vs. Teen Titans
movies.title_long: Teen Titans Go! Vs. Teen Titans (2019)
movies.summary: The comedic modern-day quintet takes on their 2003 counterparts when villains from each of their worlds join forces to pit the two Titan teams against each other. They'll need to set aside their differences and work together to combat Trigon, Hexagon, Santa Claus and time itself in order to save the universe.
